    <bug_when>2015-09-08 14:45:12 -0400</bug_when>
    <thetext>That argument does not make much sense.to me. The default font needs to work well with the default font rendering settings. It does not follow that it is somehow unsuitable because it doesn&apos;t work equally well with _all_ possible font rendering settings.

But in any case, we are investigating replacing Cantarell as the default font (for other reasons).</thetext>
